profile: Cam is a qualified home inspector, having served the Kingston area for 15 years. His three decades in the construction and renovation trade serve him well when doing home inspections. Having recently moved to Lanark County, he is now serving clients in the Lanark, Perth, Almonte, Smiths Falls and Carleton Place area, though he will continue to write his "Ask the Inspector" and "Green Tech-the series" columns, which appear weekly in the Kingston Whig Standard.
